WEBVTT

01:32:34.624 --> 01:32:36.333
They thought we were dead...

01:32:36.749 --> 01:32:39.541
and threw us on the railway tracks...

01:32:40.708 --> 01:32:42.041
mom was crushed to pieces...

01:32:42.999 --> 01:32:43.999
but I survived...

01:32:45.912 --> 01:32:47.745
I became a thief for him.

01:32:49.001 --> 01:32:52.001
All these days I've been stealing his money.

01:32:53.501 --> 01:32:55.584
After so many years, they found me...

01:32:56.251 --> 01:32:58.293
but he put his mind in mine.
